                &lt;p>&#xD;
                    &lt;em>Table 1 - Risks for the adoption of iterative development&lt;/em>&#xD;
                &lt;/p>&#xD;
            &lt;/blockquote>&#xD;
        &lt;/blockquote>&#xD;
    &lt;/blockquote>&#xD;
&lt;/blockquote></mainDescription>
